<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Artist Profile</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.6.0/css/all.min.css">
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js" defer></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" defer></script>

    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Poppins');

        html {
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        html::-webkit-scroller {
            display: none;
        }

        #main-nav {
            background-color: transparent;
        }

        section {
            height: 100vh;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #FFF0D1;
            background-position: center;
            color: #3B3030;
            padding-bottom: 50px;
        }

        .content-wrapper {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .main {
            flex: 1;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #3B3030;
            position: static;
            width: 100%;
            padding: 20px 100px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            z-index: 99;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #FFF0D1;
            user-select: none;
        }

        .navigation a {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #FFF0D1;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-left: 40px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .navigation a::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            bottom: -6px;
            width: 100%;
            height: 3px;
            background: #FFF0D1;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transform-origin: right;
            transform: scaleX(0);
            transition: transform .5s;
        }

        .navigation a:hover::after {
            transform-origin: left;
            transform: scaleX(1);
            transition: transform .5s;
        }

        .navigation .back_button {
            width: 130px;
            height: 50px;
            background: transparent;
            border: 2px solid #FFF0D1;
            border-radius: 6px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #FFF0D1;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-left: 40px;
            transition: .5s;
        }

        .navigation .back_button:hover {
            background: #FFF0D1;
            color: #162938;
        }

        #home::before {
            content: "";
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: url('/portfoliobackground.png');
            background-position: top;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-size: cover;
            background-attachment: fixed;
            opacity: 0.4;
            z-index: -1;
        }

        i {
            color: #3B3030;
        }

        .container {
            color: #3B3030;
            width: 600px;
            margin-top: 150px;
            margin-left: 70px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .container_2 {
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        #about .img-hero {
            height: 500px;
            width: 500px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: block;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .card-icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
        }

        .block {
            height: 10px;
            width: 80px;
            background-color: #3B3030;
            margin-right: auto;
            margin-left: auto;
            border-radius: 4px;
            border-color: #3B3030;
            border-width: 4px;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            opacity: 0.5;
        }

        .footer_bottom {
            background-color: #3B3030;
            color: #FFF0D1;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            width: 100%;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .footer_bottom {
                font-size: 0.9rem;
                padding: 15px 10px;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .footer_bottom {
                flex-direction: column;
                font-size: 0.8rem;
                padding: 20px 10px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="content-wrapper">
        <header>
            <h2 class="logo">Logo</h2>
            <nav class="navigation">
                <a href="/explore">Home</a>
            </nav>
        </header>
        <main>
            <section id="home">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-lg-6-custom-col">
                            <ul class="list-inline">
                                <li class="list-inline-item">
                                    <a href="#profile.html">
                                        <i class="fas fa-user border border-dark rounded-circle p-2"
                                            style="color:#3B3030;"></i>
                                    </a>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                            <h1 class="display-3">I am <%=userDetails.username %>
                            </h1>
                            <p class="lead">
                            <p>Crafting music that resonates deeply, I explore the connections between sound, emotion,
                                and storytelling</p>
                            </p>
                            <div class="d-flex">
                                <a href="" class="btn btn-outline-dark mr-3 p-2"
                                    style="color:#FFF0D1; background-color:#3B3030;">My Portfolio</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section id="about" class="bg-light">
                <div class="container_2">
                    <div class="row align-items-center">
                        <div class="col-lg-6 spacing">
                            <img src="<%= userDetails.avatar %>" alt="Artist photo" class="img-fluid img-hero">
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-6">
                            <h2 class="display-4">Hi! I am <%=userDetails.username %>, an Artist on Rap Clash.
                            </h2>
                            <p class="lead">
                                My music is a fusion of soulful lyrics and energetic beats, aiming to uplift and
                                inspire. Each song I create is an invitation for listeners to feel, connect, and let
                                go.
                            </p>
                            <a href="#" class="btn btn-dark p-2">Know Me</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section id="dynamics" class="bg-light">
                <div class="container_3">
                    <div class="text-center pt-5">
                        <h2 class="display-4 pt-5">DYNAMICS</h2>
                        <p class="lead">
                            My work is a journey through sound, where each song is crafted to evoke emotion and tell
                            a story. From soulful melodies to high-energy beats, I strive to create music that
                            resonates on a personal level with every listener
                            Iâ€™m dedicated to pushing the boundaries of my art and creating a sound that feels both
                            timeless and fresh.
                        </p>
                        <div class="block"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-lg-4 mb-4">
                            <div class="card text-center p-5">
                                <i class="fas fa-camera card-icon mb-2" style="color: black;"></i>
                                <h5 class="card-title">
                                    SCORES
                                </h5>
                                <p class="card-text">
                                <p>The points I have scored :<%=userDetails.points%>
                                </p>
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>
        <footer class="footer_bottom">
            <a href="home.ejs" style="color:#FFF0D1;">Copyright@webster.com </a>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>

</html>